[Course_Description]
The best leaders and managers are also incredible coaches. Coaching is all about elevating each team member to be the best person that they can be in their role. In this course, Dr. Eric Zackrison explains how to go from manager to coach. Eric covers the foundations of effective coaching. He presents a pre-work guide to help you assess your team and set the stage for effective coaching. Eric shows you how to create a supportive climate and foster collaboration. He shares how to create effective coaching sessions that can help you close the gaps in your team. In closing, Eric describes how to follow best practices, measure your success, set goals, and prioritize effectively. This course was created by Madecraft. We are pleased to host this training in our library.